column1: blxpQuery-from DatabaseKeyword where BLXP_BATCH_ID= :batch and BLXP_CLCL_ID= :clmid

column7: MEME.MEME_REL FROM FC_CMC_GRGR_GROUP GRGR JOIN FC_CMC_SBSB_SUBSC  SBSB ON GRGR.GRGR_CK= SBSB.GRGR_CK JOIN FC_CMC_MEME_MEMBER MEME ON SBSB.SBSB_CK = MEME.SBSB_CK JOIN FC_CMC_SGSG_SUB_GROUP SGSG ON GRGR.GRGR_CK= SGSG.GRGR_CK JOIN FC_CMC_CSPI_CS_PLAN CSCS ON CSCS.GRGR_CK = GRGR.GRGR_CK JOIN FC_CMC_PDPD_PRODUCT PDPD ON CSCS.PDPD_ID =PDPD.PDPD_ID JOIN CU_ARGUS_DBP_AFA_INB_FILE_HIST INB ON INB.SBSCR_ID= SBSB.SBSB_ID WHERE SBSB.SBSB_ID= :sbsb AND CSCS.CSPI_ID= :cscs AND GRGR.GRGR_ID = :grgr  AND INB.CLM_ID= :clmid AND MEME.MEME_sfx= :memsfx
